#define OSSL_IMPL_SK2ARY ( name,
type   ) 
Value:
VALUE                                           \
ossl_##name##_sk2ary(STACK_OF(type) *sk)        \
{                                               \
    type *t;                                    \
    int i, num;                                 \
    VALUE ary;                                  \
                                                \
    if (!sk) {                                  \
        OSSL_Debug("empty sk!");                \
        return Qnil;                            \
    }                                           \
    num = sk_##type##_num(sk);                  \
    if (num < 0) {                              \
        OSSL_Debug("items in sk < -1???");      \
        return rb_ary_new();                    \
    }                                           \
    ary = rb_ary_new2(num);                     \
                                                \
    for (i=0; i<num; i++) {                     \
        t = sk_##type##_value(sk, i);           \
        rb_ary_push(ary, ossl_##name##_new(t)); \
    }                                           \
    return ary;                                 \
}
